'From Squeak3.9alpha of ''2 November 2004'' [latest update: #6603] on 1 April 2005 at 9:17:24 pm'!"Change Set:		6605-FixeScrollbarsDate:			1 April 2005Author:			stéphane ducassefixing old instance of scrollbars"!"Postscript:Fix the scrollbar instances in the image"| candidates |candidates := ScrollBar allInstances         select: [:m | m slotName = 'scrollBar' & m model isKindOf:ScrollPane].candidates   do: [:c |      c instVarNamed: 'slotName' put: 'vScrollBar'.      c instVarNamed: 'setValueSelector' put: #vScrollBarValue:]!